---
layout: layouts/home.njk
title: designwithkat — Senior Digital Product Designer
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="home-hero">
  <div class="home-hero-content">
<h1 class="home-heading" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.5s">Understanding <em>people</em> <svg class="hero-icon hero-icon--person" width="28" height="24" viewBox="0 0 28 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle class="hero-icon-head" cx="14" cy="7" r="5" stroke="#ff4d6d" stroke-width="1.5"/><path class="hero-icon-shoulders" d="M3 23 C3 15 25 15 25 23" stroke="#ff4d6d" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><br>Shaping products<span class="hero-dot">.</span></h1>
    <p class="home-body" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.3s">Over ten years designing digital experiences, from early-stage startups to global brands. I turn complex problems into clear, usable products.</p>
    <div class="home-cta-group" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.45s">
      <a href="#work" class="home-cta">See Case Studies</a>
      <a href="#experience" class="home-cta-link">View Work History</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Selected Work -->
<section class="home-work" id="work">
  <div class="home-work-header" data-animate>
    <p class="home-work-eyebrow">Selected Work</p>
    <h2 class="home-work-heading">Design Stories</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="home-cards-wrap">
  <div class="home-cards" id="home-cards" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.15s">

    <a href="/toyota/" class="home-card home-card--toyota">
      <div class="home-card-meta">
        <span class="home-card-company">Toyota Connected (EU)</span>
        <h3 class="home-card-title">Making Smart Charging effortless</h3>
        <p class="home-card-desc">Revamping the Smart Charging setup experience to simplify onboarding for Toyota EV owners.</p>
        <span class="home-card-cta">Read Case Study →</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-card-demo">
        <img src="/assets/Toyota/smart charging1.png" alt="Smart Charging app" class="home-card-phone-img home-card-phone-img--peek" />
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/shell/" class="home-card home-card--shell">
      <div class="home-card-meta">
        <span class="home-card-company">Shell Energy</span>
        <h3 class="home-card-title">Energy insights. Real saving potential.</h3>
        <p class="home-card-desc">Creating Shell Energy's first customer mobile app, empowering users to manage their home energy usage.</p>
        <span class="home-card-cta">Read Case Study →</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-card-demo">
        <img src="/assets/Shell/energy assistant.png" alt="Shell Energy app" class="home-card-phone-img home-card-phone-img--padded" />
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/sonnen/" class="home-card home-card--sonnen">
      <div class="home-card-meta">
        <span class="home-card-company">Sonnen</span>
        <h3 class="home-card-title">A smarter way to own your energy.</h3>
        <p class="home-card-desc">Designing the experience for Sonnen's home battery ecosystem, helping users take control of their energy independence.</p>
        <span class="home-card-cta">Read Case Study →</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-card-demo">
        <img src="/assets/sonnen/sonnen2.png" alt="Sonnen app" class="home-card-phone-img home-card-phone-img--full" />
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/gensec-health/" class="home-card home-card--gensec home-card--relative">
      <div class="home-card-nda">
        <span class="home-card-nda-icon">🔒</span>
        <span class="home-card-nda-label">Under NDA</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-card-meta">
        <span class="home-card-company">Health-Tech Startup</span>
        <h3 class="home-card-title">Making health data work for everyone.</h3>
        <p class="home-card-desc">Building a platform that connects patients and clinicians through clear, actionable health insights.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-card-demo">
        <img src="/assets/sonnen/Gensec Health/gensec1.png" alt="Gensec Health app" class="home-card-phone-img" />
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>
  <div class="home-cards-dots" id="home-cards-dots"></div>
  </div>
</section>

