<!-- About -->
<section class="home-about">
  <div class="home-about-photo" data-animate>
    <div class="home-about-photo-placeholder"></div>
    <div class="home-about-badge">
      <span class="home-about-badge-number">10+</span>
      <span class="home-about-badge-label">years experience</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="home-about-content" data-animate style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
    <p class="home-about-eyebrow">About</p>
    <h2 class="home-about-heading">Designing with care and clarity</h2>
    <p class="home-about-name">Hi! I'm Kat 👋</p>
    <p class="home-about-body">I've been a digital designer for the past ten years, building on an earlier career in digital content, media and marketing. Having originally trained in design, I felt over time a strong pull back to creating.</p>
    <p class="home-about-body">I'm motivated by the problem-solving side of UX, understanding what people genuinely think and feel about a product, and translating those insights into decisions that support business goals. I value close collaboration and building trust within teams, particularly when navigating complex challenges. Much of my work sits within data-rich, regulated industries, where clarity, alignment, and careful thinking matter.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="home-traits">
    <div class="home-trait">
      <p class="home-trait-title">📊 Simplifying Complexity</p>
      <p class="home-trait-body">I'm particularly drawn to complex products and systems, where careful research and clear thinking can turn ambiguity into simple, usable experiences.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-trait">
      <p class="home-trait-title">🔍 Diligent</p>
      <p class="home-trait-body">I'm a diligent and conscientious designer — I couldn't approach tasks half-heartedly. I care deeply about what I build and am genuinely passionate about advocating for the user.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-trait">
      <p class="home-trait-title">🔄 Adaptable</p>
      <p class="home-trait-body">I adapt quickly as teams, priorities, and problems evolve, having successfully navigated change across multiple industries and platforms.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-trait">
      <p class="home-trait-title">💬 Collaborative</p>
      <p class="home-trait-body">I value close collaboration and building trust within teams, and across several roles I've proactively identified gaps in ways of working and helped to implement meaningful improvements.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Work History -->
<section class="home-experience" id="experience">
  <div class="home-experience-header" data-animate>
    <p class="home-experience-eyebrow">Experience</p>
    <h2 class="home-experience-heading">Work History</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="home-timeline">
    {% for item in experience %}
    <div class="home-timeline-entry" data-animate>
      <div class="home-timeline-left">
        <span class="home-timeline-dates">{{ item.dates }}</span>
        <span class="home-timeline-company">{{ item.company }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="home-timeline-center">
        <div class="home-timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="home-timeline-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="home-timeline-right">
        <h3 class="home-timeline-role">{{ item.role }}</h3>
        {% if item.bullets %}
        <ul class="home-timeline-bullets">
          {% for bullet in item.bullets %}
          <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% else %}
        <p class="home-timeline-desc">{{ item.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="home-timeline-pills">
          {% for activity in item.activities %}
          <span class="home-timeline-pill">{{ activity }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
